Duff Till Dawn - Season 1, Episode 4




Super Cake Heroes

As the sun sets on Duff Goldman's shop, he challenges two teams of bakers to create the best superhero cake they can before the sun comes up. Will Lachlan Oliver's Super Lumenator light up the world or will Kimberly Bailey's Super Chi-Weenie save a family of lady bugs from certain doom? Duff and guest judges Geof Manthorne and Carrie Keagan will award the golden whisk to the cake that reigns supreme.




Original Air Date: 19-Feb-2015
